highlights.text: “SOS (feat. Aloe Blacc)” by Avicii and Aloe Blacc is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 152 spots at #5.
“Boy With Luv (feat. Halsey)” by BTS and Halsey is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #1.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 119 weeks straight.
